{
  "stem": "24195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we talked, but he didn't-- he was two years younger.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he was not in the same-- in the same environment that I was in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, you know, I couldn't even-- I couldn't even have a nice playtime, leisure time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- when I-- after school, when I wanted to go out and, you know, ride on my bike-- we lived in a-- we lived then-- by that time, we had recovered from the clinic, you know.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Had-- our, our financial, economic situation had stabilized.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in a-- we were in another nice-- yeah, we were in a nice apartment at that time when I went to school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you, of course, go to school wherever your-- in what district you live in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were-- no, we were well-- we were well-situated then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as a-- it still-- I, I, you know, I could not-- it was difficult.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The, the issue of being half-Jewish would come up anytime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because now, at an age when you're 14, 15, 16 years old, people think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, you're more mature.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, then you think about the differences in-- between races and between-- and between different people, you know, the-- what makes people different.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my classmates would always taunt me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, you know--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Make-- you know, make, make insulting remarks to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember one day when I had just gotten a new bicycle-- which was quite an accomplishment because you couldn't get any more bicycles during the war.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were used [LAUGHS] for the military, too, for some reason.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was, like, '41.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But somehow my mother had gotten a very nice new bike for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was riding around, trying to, to show it off to my classmates.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
